        Creates laptop entity object with the specified params
        Parameters:
        price - - price of the laptop
        batteryCapacity - - capacity of the laptop's battery in Amper-hours
        operationSystem - - laptop's operation system name (null if no operation system)
        memoryROM - - laptop's memory ROM in GBytes
        systemMemory - - laptop's RAM in MBytes
        cpu - - laptop's CPU in GHerz
        displayInchs - - laptop's display diagonal length in inches
